Activity Labels

WALKING (value 1): subject was walking during the test
WALKING_UPSTAIRS (value 2): subject was walking up a staircase during the test
WALKING_DOWNSTAIRS (value 3): subject was walking down a staircase during the test
SITTING (value 4): subject was sitting during the test
STANDING (value 5): subject was standing during the test
LAYING (value 6): subject was laying down during the test

Variables Used in my script

 x_test  - Values of all variables
 y_test - Activity ids of test data
 subject_test - Subject ids of all testing set observations
 x_train - Values of all variables, training set
 y_train - Activity ids of all training data
 subject_train - subject ids of all training set observations
 features - List of all variables name in the second column 
 Activites - Name of the activities
 train_final - Combined y_train,subject_train and x_train data
 test_final - combined y_test,subject_test and y_train data
 all_data - combined testing and traning data
 reqcols - Names of required columns viz. all columns with mean and standard deviations values, activity_id and subject_id
 sub_all_data - subset of all_data with required columns
 data1 - dataset with mean values of all the variables in sub_all_data aggregated by activity_id and subject_id
 tidy - tidy data with descritive name of activity ids



 
 
